  "title": "CLEANING SERVICES MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<p>· Supervise the conduct of the cleaners and the ability to manage a team</p>\n<p>· Ensure proper maintenance and upkeep of all client's premises</p>\n<p>· To inspect assigned areas for cleanliness and for adequate cleaning supplies</p>\n<p>· Arranging duty roster and assisting operations manager on duties</p>\n<p>· Need to travel from site to site and assist in the cleaning duties</p>\n<p>· Adhoc duties as assigned</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Supervisory or cleaning experience</p>\n<p>· Presentable and can speak well</p>\n<p>· Comfortable with rotating shifts, night shift</p>\n<p>· Able to work on weekends and Public holidays</p>\n<p>· Salary ：$3100 - $4500 (including allowances, incentives)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested please email detailed resumes with work experience and attached a most recent photo to rachel@jalley.com.sg</p>\n<p>Ow Ting Ting (R2094613)</p>\n<p>Jobs Alley Pte Ltd (21C0599)</p>",
