    "description": "<p>J &amp; S Management Pte Ltd is a personalized on-call housekeeping service catering to homes and offices. We are a social enterprise and an inclusive business providing quality service towards our valued customers.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our Mission is to make the world a better place, one clean home and office at a time. To ensure competency, honesty, courtesy, and intergrity of the housekeepers. We deploy, in order to ensure the safety and satisfaction of our customers and clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We wish to elevate the economic status of our workers, giving them the opportunity to earn more and have a decent living without having to leave their families.</p>",
